stories_text_raw:
As a Data User, I want to process deletions for a specific date, so that I can manage data effectively.
As a Data User, I want to access raw agency published files, so that I can utilize the data for my needs.
As a Data User, I want to see updated financial assistance data, so that I can stay informed about the latest financial information.
As a UI Designer, I want to redesign the Resources page, so that users can easily find the resources they need.
As a UI Designer, I want to report to agencies about user testing, so that they can be informed about the testing process.
As a UI Designer, I want to move on to the next round of page edits, so that I can continue improving the user interface.
As a DevOps Engineer, I want to provide useful data, so that the team can make informed decisions.
As a Broker User, I want to sync D1 file generation with FPDS data load, so that data is consistent and up-to-date.
As a Broker User, I want to derive the FundingAgencyCode, so that I can accurately identify the funding agency.
As a Broker User, I want to map FederalActionObligation properly to the Atom Feed, so that data is accurately represented.
As an Agency User, I want to submit data, so that I can provide the necessary information.
As an Agency User, I want to include a large number of flexfields, so that I can provide detailed information.
As an Agency User, I want to know when submission periods start and end, so that I can plan and submit data on time.
As a FABS User, I want to access published FABS files, so that I can utilize the data for my needs.
As a FABS User, I want to see correct status labels on the Submission Dashboard, so that I can easily track the status of submissions.
As a Developer, I want to log better, so that I can effectively debug and troubleshoot issues.
As a Developer, I want to add updates to FABS submission, so that I can improve the submission process.
As a Developer, I want to update the FABS sample file, so that users have accurate and up-to-date information.
As a Developer, I want to prevent duplicate transactions from being published, so that data is accurate and reliable.
As a Tester, I want to test features in environments other than Staging, so that I can ensure the features work as expected in different environments.
As an Owner, I want to reset the environment to only take Staging MAX permissions, so that I can control access to the environment.
As an Owner, I want to create a user testing summary from the UI SME, so that I can track and analyze user testing results.
